cdata.name: RChain
cdata.desc:
The RChain platform supports multiple blockchains both public and private, even on the same node. These blockchains are secured by the type of consensus protocol - proof-of-stake enabling the blockchains to interact securely and predictably. TheSmart contracts are verified on Rchain and arewritten in RhoLang.Rholang contracts run on the Rho Virtual Machine - a concurrent execution engine that allows the applications to achieve significant speed and scalability.

RHOC is an ERC-20 Tokenthat will work as the access tokento those who want to support the development of the RChain Platform. It represents the value that the early adopters gave it by supporting the RChain project.
